verbose_text: In S2, GFT505 did not reduce 2-h glucose (-0.52 mmol/L [-infinity to 0.61], P = 0.18) but led to a significant decrease of homeostasis model assessment of insulin resistance (-31.4% [-infinity to 12.5], P = 0.001), fasting plasma glucose (-0.37 mmol/L [-infinity to -0.10], P = 0.01) and fructosamine (-3.6% [-infinity to -0.20], P = 0.02).
